      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "Used car in fair condition. It runs and drives, but it shows noticeable wear from age and use. The interior and exterior are presentable but have cosmetic flaws, and you should expect maintenance or repairs over time. A practical option if you want something usable at a more affordable price.",
