    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Poor-condition vehicle being sold as-is. It shows heavy cosmetic wear inside and out, with visible blemishes, worn surfaces, and clear signs of long-term use. Expect deferred maintenance and likely mechanical issues, so this is best suited for a handy buyer, project use, or someone looking for a budget car rather than a turn-key daily driver.",
