      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition example that offers a lot to like without pretending to be perfect. It shows nicely overall, with a clean presentation inside and out, and it\u2019s clearly been cared for, though you should expect some normal signs of age and use. A strong, enjoyable car for someone who wants a very respectable driver at a more realistic price point.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition example that presents well and should be a satisfying car to own and enjoy. The exterior is attractive overall with normal age-related cosmetic wear you would expect on a used vehicle, but it remains well-kept and far nicer than a tired driver. The interior is similarly in good usable shape, showing some wear from use but remaining complete, comfortable, and presentable. This is not a fully restored or concours-level car, but it is a solid, appealing example for someone who wants a nice driver without taking on a major project.",
      "price": 31200.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with solid value for the money. This vehicle is best suited for buyers seeking a budget-friendly option with everyday utility and plenty of life left for the right owner. A practical choice for a commuter, project, or spare vehicle, offered at an approachable price by a seller committed to straightforward representation.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option that could make a great daily runabout, first car, or handy project. It offers real value for someone who wants dependable basic transport without spending a fortune. Priced honestly and ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and dependable drivetrain behavior. Starts up, moves out well, and has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes upkeep approachable for an enthusiast or handy owner. Not a show car, but it offers real utility, good road presence, and a great entry point for someone wanting an affordable platform with usable performance and plenty of life left in the core components. Priced to reflect condition while still offering a lot of car for the money.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap driver. Runs, moves, gets the job done. Rough around the edges, priced to sell now.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s not pretending to be a showroom piece\u2014it\u2019s a soulful machine with personality, presence, and the kind of lived-in story that makes every drive feel a little more memorable. Perfect for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly ride with standout attitude, weekend-project potential, or a dependable companion with plenty of grit left to give. If you\u2019re looking for something affordable, distinctive, and full of possibility, this one is easy to imagine making your own.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers an accessible entry point for anyone seeking basic transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values price and practicality, but it still presents a chance to get behind the wheel without stretching the budget. A sensible option for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone looking for inexpensive everyday utility.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    }
